==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Litigate
<hw>Lit"i*gate</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To carry on a suit by
judicial process.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Litigation</ent>⟦br⟧
